ALPINE1
Hi! I'm an Architectural Engineering undergrad student that enjoys building cities in Minecraft. My degree concentrates on structural engineering, heritage conservation, sustainable building design, and architectural technology.

TEXTURES
CubedPack https://cubed.community/texturepack/
Requires Java V1.14.4 & Optifine V1.14.4 https://optifine.net/ (30 second install)
--------------------------------------------------------
CUBED COMMUNITY MINECRAFT SERVER
Server IP: play.cubed.community - Java 1.14.4 only
Chat w/other builders & see player's builds: https://cubed.community/discord
Come build with us, or just use a personal plot to test out an idea! We provide common building tools to help you bring ideas to life. 

Apply for an advanced rank w/Terra city building permissions: https://cubed.community/apply/
Terra city building requires Builder (I)
Andea requires Specialist (I)

Guest - Builder (I-IV) - Specialist (I-II)
Plots - Terra city, Large plots - Andea creators & talented individuals
